					<![CDATA[
						 <p>For those who were here when it happened, I hope you all enjoyed the April Foolery.</p> <p>For those who are viewing this in the <em><strong><span style="color: blue">FUTURE</span></strong></em>, this was what the Front Page of the SCP Wiki looked like on Apr. 1, 2020. Simply put, our April Fools theme was &quot;Super Cool Plants&quot;, a throwback to <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/april-fools-2014">Super Cute Pets</a> of 2014.</p> <p>Many thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1229263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1585801619" alt="Roget" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1229263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" >Roget</a></span> for coming up with the idea and writing the edits for <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-031">SCP-031</a>, <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-426">SCP-426</a>, and <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-999">SCP-999</a>, along with <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-600-co">SCP-600-CO</a>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3075960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1585801619" alt="stormbreath" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3075960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" >stormbreath</a></span> for making the wonderful theme, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/procyonlotor" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=778357&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1585801619" alt="ProcyonLotor" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=778357)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/procyonlotor" >ProcyonLotor</a></span> for giving us the go-ahead.</p> <p>Check out <a 